WEBVTT

00:02.556 --> 00:04.141
Previously on "The Path"...

00:04.142 --> 00:05.477
‐ The only experience I've had
is with one other

00:05.478 --> 00:06.813
super‐closeted guy
at the church.

00:06.814 --> 00:08.525
‐ Is it Arnie Phillips?

00:08.526 --> 00:12.115
‐ Tonight I want to introduce
the Guardian

00:12.116 --> 00:16.415
who will tend this corner
of the world, Felicia Pickard.

00:16.416 --> 00:18.503
‐ You should've left him
in the ground.

00:18.504 --> 00:21.425
‐ I need you to find
your way back.

00:21.426 --> 00:23.847
‐ You have to tell Eddie
the truth about Steve.

00:23.848 --> 00:27.605
‐ Vera has found some old
diaries of Steve's,

00:27.606 --> 00:30.360
and she thinks you wrote
"The Ladder," or part of it.

00:30.361 --> 00:33.032
‐ She claims Steve stole
the religion from her,

00:33.033 --> 00:35.287
but that's not what
made us cut her off.

00:35.288 --> 00:37.165
It was when she hurt her child.

00:37.166 --> 00:38.961
The poor girl is probably
scarred for life.

00:38.962 --> 00:42.217
‐ I don't need
a secular liaison.

00:42.218 --> 00:45.808
‐ Are you firing me?
‐ I guess I am.

00:45.809 --> 00:49.106
‐ He loves me. The answer
is to find more JPs,

00:49.107 --> 00:52.447
make them my followers,
and then take them with me.

